comments.body: Sometimes immature hawks are very tolerant of people. Some of them have not yet learned that many people are dangerous to them.
It was about 25 degrees outside, and that hawk appeared unbothered by my presence.
tail is too long proportionally for a Red-tailed Hawk or any Buteo. The streaking on the upper chest area is also not correct. This appears to be an immature Cooper's Hawk.
